description: Concrete Cuisine is a fully licensed gourmet food truck with the ability to service most outdoor functions.  Our truck comes on-site and cooks fresh food to order for all of your guests.  We will be out in Detroit on a daily basis serving Fresh Eats on the Streets!  We are available for numerous events including: graduation parties, corporate lunches and events, tailgating, block parties, nightlife, sporting events... Concrete Cuisine's chefs can execute their eclectic menu for your party.
name: Concrete Cuisine
